(54, 1, '2012-05-13 15:31:06', '2012-05-13 19:31:06', '<p style="text-align: left;">Welcome to Ragamalika.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">Carnatic Music is the classical music of Southern India. It is based a complex system of ragam and talam. The melodic foundation is the ragam. Ragam is basically the scale. The seven notes of the scale are Sa, Ri, Ga, Ma, Pa, Dha, and Ni.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">Ragamalika is a garland of Ragas.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">RAGAMALIKA is a nonprofit cultural organization registered in VA USA. This is the 25th anniversary of this organization. It was started by Mrs.Maragatham Ramaswamy in 1987. Mrs.Maragatham holds a degree in music from the carnatic music college of Chennai.  All of her advanced students are also wonderful musicians who continue to hone their craft as they perform locally, regionally, nationally and internationally.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">We are located at 25588,Fishers hill Ct., Chantilly VA. Mrs. Maragatham Ramaswamy has been performing and teaching music for over 25 years in Fairfax County and now in Loudon County.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;" align="center">We stress the musical foundations of reading and theory, while using modern music genres and technology to assist you in exploring your musicality. We have students from age 5 through 75, and she teaches all levels and abilities. So don''t be shy; give your music a try!</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '51-autosave', '', '', '2012-05-13 15:31:06', '2012-05-13 19:31:06', '', 51, 'http://bramkaslp01/bramkas/?p=54', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(55, 1, '2012-05-13 15:29:05', '2012-05-13 19:29:05', 'Welcome to Ragamalika.\r\n<p align="center">Carnatic Music is the classical music of Southern India. It is based a complex system of ragam and talam. The melodic foundation is the ragam. Ragam is basically the scale. The seven notes of the scale are Sa, Ri, Ga, Ma, Pa, Dha, and Ni.</p>\r\n<p align="center">Ragamalika is a garland of Ragas.</p>\r\n<p align="center">RAGAMALIKA is a nonprofit cultural organization registered in VA USA. This is the 25th anniversary of this organization. It was started by Mrs.Maragatham Ramaswamy in 1987. Mrs.Maragatham holds a degree in music from the carnatic music college of Chennai.  All of her advanced students are also wonderful musicians who continue to hone their craft as they perform locally, regionally, nationally and internationally.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="center">We are located at 25588,Fishers hill Ct., Chantilly VA. Mrs. Maragatham Ramaswamy has been performing and teaching music for over 25 years in Fairfax County and now in Loudon County.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p align="center">We stress the musical foundations of reading and theory, while using modern music genres and technology to assist you in exploring your musicality. We have students from age 5 through 75, and she teaches all levels and abilities. So don''t be shy; give your music a try!</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '51-revision-3', '', '', '2012-05-13 15:29:05', '2012-05-13 19:29:05', '', 51, 'http://bramkaslp01/bramkas/?p=55', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
